    <TimelineItem
      date="2024-2026"
      title="Republican Voter Suppression Agenda for 2026 Midterms"
      description="GOP-controlled states advancing coordinated voter suppression: eliminating no-excuse absentee voting, ending automatic voter registration, shortening early voting periods, new certification disruption rules (blocked by courts in 2024, being retried). Multi-pronged strategy: federal raids + state legislation + voter suppression = comprehensive election rigging apparatus."
    />
    <TimelineItem
      date="MAR 2025"
      title="Executive Order Attempting to Control State Elections (Blocked by Courts)"
      description="Trump issued sweeping executive order attempting to control state election procedures, including requiring citizenship proof for federal voter registration. Federal courts blocked major portions on constitutional grounds. Trump's first attempt to federalize elections was stopped by courts. He then escalated to direct 'takeover' threats."
    />
    <TimelineItem
      date="JAN 2025"
      badge="UNLAWFUL"
      badgeType="catastrophic"
      title="Fired 17 Inspector Generals (Ruled Unlawful)"
      description="Trump fired 17 Inspector Generals across federal agencies in coordinated purge of independent oversight. Why this enables election rigging: IGs provide oversight of DOJ and FBI. Removing them allows Trump loyalists to conduct election interference (like Georgia raid) without accountability. Legal status: Federal judge ruled firings violated federal law. Ordered reinstatement and back pay."
    />
  </TimelineSection>

  <!-- Related: Installing Loyalists -->
