      badgeType="serious"
      title="Federal Courts Block Election Executive Order"
      description="Federal courts blocked Trump's March 2025 executive order attempting to federalize election procedures. Courts ruled citizenship proof requirement unconstitutional. Multiple judges cited separation of powers and federalism concerns. Pattern: Every time Trump tries to federalize elections, courts stop him. Trump responded by escalating to direct 'nationalize voting' demands."
    />
