      title="States Refuse Federal Takeover Attempts"
      description="Multiple states refusing to comply with DOJ voter roll demands and federal interference. Arizona refused voter roll demands. California resisting federal pressure. Multiple states citing state sovereignty. Fulton County filing lawsuit over FBI raid. Status: States are resisting, but Trump administration escalating pressure through lawsuits and raids."
    />
  </TimelineSection>

