      attribution="Adrian Fontes — Arizona Secretary of State · January 29, 2026 (responding to Georgia raid) · Current election official warning of active election rigging in real-time"
    />
    <VoiceCard
      quote="These raids on election offices are unprecedented and dangerous. This is not how democracies function."
      attribution="Brad Raffensperger — Georgia Secretary of State (Republican) · January 2026 · Same official Trump pressured in 2020 now facing FBI raids"
    />
